MBOMBELA – Three people were tragically killed this morning at around 04:00 in Matsulu. Department of Safety and Security spokesman Moeti Mmusi said that this happened when the bakkie they were travelling in went off the bridge and crashed after the driver allegedly lost control of the vehicle. He said three people died at the scene.
